name: Magazine HeadBand
description: This is piece is my favourite out of all of them. It is funny because I just created because I needed to get rid of my magazine collection and I wore it school the next day and everyone thought it was really cute. It is a really unique product that stands out and makes a big statement. Attached to elastic band with a little pearl in the middle it is very simple and easy to put on. It has a layer of glue on it so it won't rip easy but I don't reccommend wearing it on a rainyday without an umbrella. If you want a certain colour scheme or a special celebrity on your piece please email me at ella_4561@hotmail.com.

name: Minnie Mouse Bow
description: This is a creation that really is a big hit. I love this one because it really switches things up a bit. It is really cute yet casual and really makes a statement with whatever you are wearing. You can request colours and I have yellow, floral and yellow lace. This piece is also attached to an elastic so your are fiddle free when you wear your piece.

name: Mini Bow
description: So I am following one of the trends of today by creating a mini bow. But I added my own touch with the checkered fabric. I love this fabric because I love picnics. They are so carefree, perfect and fun. This is what I am trying to portray in this item. With a precise cut and cut design, I want to make it fun to wear accesories and something that you want to do. This piece also is attached to an elastic and can be made in many different fabrics such as floral, yellow and yellow lace. For any other colour suggestions please email me at ella_4561@hotmail.com.

name: Red Rose Hair Piece
description: This piece was inspired from looking at my neighbours rose garden everyday and just being tempted to pick one up and put one in my hair. Roses have such an elegant romantic feel to them and thats why I love them so much. I made this piece to make you feel pretty and very feminine looking. Thats what every girl wants right? This piece is attached to a hair pin but if you would prefer to have it on a headband just email me and you can pay and extra 50 cents.

name: Hesian Belt
description: I made this item because I truly hate belts. They are so uncomfortable but look so cute. So I decided to make a light weight belt that looks cute but is so comfy aswell. Well this is it girls. Show off the smallest part of your body in the comfiest way possible with this belt. The hesian fabric is really earthy and super comfy. If you are interested in buying please send me your measurements prior to purchasing and we can figure it out from there.
